snippet.textDisplay:
I am Bangladeshi and am here from a facebook reel. 
I am suppperrrrr dupppereer pleased,because here I have found all the tastes. The Classical touch,the beautiful relation among traditional and modern instruments,the composition everything...... 
And I was not bored for a single moment. I loved the instrument parts also!
The transition starts from 5:59 justtttttttt❤️🔥🔥🔥🔥🔥

I don’t know what should I write,It's beyond all the compliments. 

Thanks everyone for making a masterpiece like this❤️
